      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "COLLINDA BLINDER (1) charged out of the boxes with a fast early split and led for much of the way before being grabbed late, finishing a 1.1 lengths second at this track over 435m in 24.66. Must come into calculations. MAD HATTER ROSE (3) had won two in a row before finishing fourth (24.78) last time at this track. Has a good record here including five wins. Some good form is emerging from her last run. Has ability and is one of the better chances. PAW INFLAME (2) has mixed form recently, finishing sixth (22.49) in a Grade 5 at Ballarat latest but did run well two back when in the frame. Well placed here and can atone this time. DR. TESSA (6) has a solid strike rate from this box.",
